<H3> <TI>   Polish Prime Minister Pawlak Holds Talks in Moscow </TI></H3>
<H4>   Chernomyrdin, Pawlak Discuss Cooperation </H4>
<F P=102> LD1503105594 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0925 GMT 15 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1503105594 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>


