<H3> <TI>   Shevardnadze, Nikolayev Discuss Army Status </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1403204894 Tbilisi First Program Television Network in 
Georgian 1900 GMT 14 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1403204894 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi First Program Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Georgian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The head of the Georgian state today met Colonel 
General Andrey Nikolayev, the commander in chief of the Russian 
