<H3> <TI>   Stepashin Hospitalized After Meeting Yeltsin </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MK1503101094 Moscow SEGODNYA in Russian 15 Mar 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> MK1503101094 </F>
