<H3> <TI>   Chornovil Seeks Rukh Approval for Candidacy </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1503002794 Kiev UNIAN in Ukrainian 2100 GMT 14 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1503002794 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev UNIAN </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Kiev -- As RUKH-PRESS reported on 14 March, NRU 
[People's Movement of Ukraine, Rukh] Chairman Vyacheslav 
Chornovil declared his readiness to stand for Ukraine's 
president in the June 1994 election if Rukh approves such a 
decision. According to him, "the program of Rukh, supported by 
the people, can become a program of transformations in Ukraine." 
The final decision on the participation of Vyacheslav Chornovil 
in the election will be approved at the second stage of the 5th 
all-Ukrainian Assembly of Rukh due to begin on 16 April. 

</TEXT>

