<F P=103> WS1603122194 </F>
<F P=104>  Vilnius ELTA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Lithuanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] It has been two weeks since Lithuania began to 
receive applications from individuals wishing to acquire a 
"Travel Document of a Stateless Person." Persons who are 
Lithuania's permanent residents, but who have no Lithuanian or 
any other citizenship, require this document when travelling 
abroad. 
  The Migration Department has reported to ELTA that only 123 
people submitted applications throughout Lithuania over the 
first 14 days. 

</TEXT>

