<H3> <TI>   Rybkin Denies Talks </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1603094494 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0839 GMT 16 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1603094494 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS parliamentary correspondent Ivan Novikov] </F>
  [Text] Moscow March 16 TASS -- State Duma Chairman Ivan 
Rybkin has denied media allegations that he had discussed the 
introduction of the economic state of emergency in the country 
with Russian officials. 
  "I have not had any discussions of this subject with 
anyone," 
Ivan Rybkin said at today's plenary meeting of the State Duma, 
responding to a question from one of the deputies. 

</TEXT>

