<F P=100> RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Security Council Official Meets Nixon </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1503130994 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1030 GMT 
15 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1503130994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Oleg Lobov, secretary of the Russian Federation 
Security Council, received former U.S. President Richard Nixon 
today. In the course of a frank conversation lasting an hour 
and a half there was discussion of topical problems relating to 
Russia's domestic politicial situation, support for Russia's 
reforms and ensuring international security and stability. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
