<H3> <TI>   Shevardnadze Discusses U.S. Visit, Abkhazia </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC1503205094 Yerevan SNARK in English 1222 GMT 15 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC1503205094 </F>
<F P=104>  Yerevan SNARK </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tbilisi, March 15 (SNARK)--The political course 
pursued by Georgia is positively appraised in the United States. 
This statement was made today by Eduard Shevardnadze at the 
Georgian Parliament sitting. 
  Sharing his impressions of the recent visit to the United 
States, he noted with satisfaction that Washington supports the 
integrity and indivisibility of Georgia. 
  Speaking about the possibility of bringing UN peacekeeping 
