<F P=100> UKRAINE </F>
<F P=101> International Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Kravchuk Meets With Nixon, Discusses `Wide Range' of Issues </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  WS1603160694 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in 
Ukrainian 1500 GMT 16 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS1603160694 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network </F>


<TEXT>
